01:08:36.738 --> 01:08:40.700
do something, you know,
that would have left his DNA.

01:08:40.908 --> 01:08:45.788
Terry Hobbs would not, at any point,
give me his DNA voluntarily, no.

01:08:46.247 --> 01:08:48.875
