She thinks I'm too wild.

01:10:13.084 --> 01:10:16.463
So she says, "You can't stay here
because you're too wild"?

01:10:18.798 --> 01:10:21.426
And I'm hung out on a limb.

01:10:21.635 --> 01:10:24.012
What's that mean,
